<h4 class="ez_pagetitle">RE: [ushahidi developers] State of the project - reassure me.</h4>
<div id="ez_msg">
<div id="ez_header">
<span class="ez_label">From:</span> &quot;Pablo A. Destefanis&quot; &lt;pdestefanis@...&gt;<br />
<span class="ez_label">Date:</span> Wed, 13 Jun 2012 09:40:25 -0400<br />
